cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with visual Simultaneously Localization and Mapping (SLAM) and appearance-based robot relocalization. It could also belong to Robotics (cs.RO) as it deals with robot relocalization. The paper also proposes a new approach using Multi-Index Hashing (MIH), which could fall under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves feature matching, which could also fall under Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
